#. 3: sound
#. 4: choice
msgctxt "talk22"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You wish to know about our water bed?\n"
"Well, as the name implies...<2.pa>it is a bed\n"
"filled with water.\n"
"It conforms to the shape of your body,\n"
"so it's like being wrapped up in a\n"
"cocoon as you sleep. Very calming.\n"
"<3.so>Oh, and its incredible cooling effect\n"
"promises a level of sleeping comfort\n"
"you simply can't find elsewhere.\n"
"Perhaps you would like to try it?<4.ch>"
msgstr ""

